org.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM notifications WHERE notifications.user_id = "$1" AND notifications.id <> "$2" AND notifications.organization_id IS NULL AND notifications.notifiable_id = "$3" AND notifications.notifiable_type = "$4" AND notifications.action = "$5" LIMIT 1
